quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  26,52,"Twara\tmurungikiye\tintumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tubutumire\tyuko yogenda ku bantu banje mugihe c’ijoro ntankeka muzo kurikiranwa"
  26,53,"Rero\tFir’auni\tyaciye\tarungika\tubutumwa\tbw’ugukoranya\tabantu\tbo mugisagara bose"
  26,54,Mu vy’ukuri abo Bayahudi n’akarwi k’abantu bakeyi cane
  26,55,Nabo n’abantu badu shavuza cane
  26,56,Natwe turi benshi mugabo turabatinya
  26,57,Duca tubakura mu mirima yabo hamwe no mumusoko y’amazi
  26,58,Nukuba kura mububiko bwabo n’ahantu habo heza cane
  26,59,Nuko rero twahaye ibisigi kuri bene Israeri
  26,60,Baca bakurikira k’ubuseruko bw’izuba
  26,61,"Mugihe zabonana ingabo zose uko ari zibiri, abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) baciye bavuga bati:- twebwe duhava dufatwa"
  26,62,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ivuga iti:- oya! mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanje ari kumwe nanje ntankeka azondongora"
  26,63,"Mumwanya twara murungikiye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ubutumwa tumubwira duti:- kubita iyo nkoni yawe kuri ico kiyaga, naco gica cigaburwamwo ibiyaga bibiri no kumpande zose haca haba nk’imisozi mininiya"
  26,64,Duca tuzana ngaho abandi bantu
  26,65,Duca turokora intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe nabo bari kumwe bose
  26,66,Hanyuma twibiza mumazi abo bandi bantu
  26,67,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tmuri\tibi\tvyose\tharimwo\ticirwa\tmugabo\tbenshi\tmuribo simubemera"
  26,68,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,69,Kandi ubasomere inkuru y’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  26,70,"Mugihe yabwira Se wiwe hamwe n’abantu biwe ati:- mbega\tmwebwe musenga ibiki"
  26,71,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- twebwe dusenga amasanamu yamisi yose"
  26,72,"Nawe avuga ati:- mbega ayo masanamu musenga arabumva mugihe muyahamagaye"
  26,73,Canke harico abamarira canke abagirira inabi
  26,74,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- ahubwo twasanze badata bacu bagira uku nyene tugira"
  26,75,"Nawe abishura ati:- mbega mwarababonye abo musenga"
  26,76,Mwebwe hamwe n’abavyeyi banyu babayeho imbere yanyu
  26,77,Ntankeka abo n’abansi banje dukuyemwo Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  26,78,Kuko ariyo yandemye kandi niyo yandongoye
  26,79,Kandi niyo intamika nukunywesha
  26,80,No mugihe nsinzikajwe n’ingwara niyo indonsa akoyokwe
  26,81,Kandi niyo izonyica hanyuma ize insubize ubuzima
  26,82,Kandi niyo nizeye yuko izongirira ikigongwe kubicumuro vyanje k’umusi w’impembo
  26,83,"Muremyi wanje numpe itegeko, kandi umpuze n’abagira ibikorwa vyiza"
  26,84,Kandi umpezagire mukuvugwa kuneza n’abantu bazoza munyuma yanje
  26,85,Kandi umpezagire mubazosigirwa ibisigi vy’imirima irimwo imihezagiro myiza yo mw’ijuru
  26,86,Kandi ugirire ikigongwe Data wanje ntankeka yari mubantu bazimiye
  26,87,Kandi ntuntetereze k’umusi wukuzurwa kw’abantu bose
  26,88,Umusi waho amatungo yabo ataco azobamarira canke ibibondo vyabo
  26,89,Dukuyemwo uwuzoba yatumbereye Imana yiwe afise umutima mwiza
  26,90,N’ijuru rizokwegerezwa ribe hafi ku bantu beranda
  26,91,N’umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu uzokwerekanwa icese kubagizi b’inabi
  26,92,"Bazobwirwa bati:- bari hehe abo mwahora musenga"
  26,93,Atari Imana mbega boshobora kubafasha canke kwifashisha bonyene
  26,94,Rero bazotabwa mumuriro udahera hamwe n’abacumuzi bagenzi babo
  26,95,Hamwe n’ingabo za Shetani zose
  26,96,Bazovuga bamwe bahora babasenga mugihe bazoba bariko baratongana bari mumuriro udahera
  26,97,"Ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  26,98,Mugihe twabagirira ineza n’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  26,99,Kandi ntibatuzimije atari babantu babi
  26,100,Natwe ntidufise abadusabira
  26,101,Canke abagenzi bwite dufise
  26,102,Iyo tuba dufise aho tugarukira twari kuba aba Isilamu
  26,103,"Ntankeka\tmuri\tibi\tvyose\tharimwo\titegero\trininiya\tmugabo\tbenshi muribo s’abemera"
  26,104,Mu vy’ukuri umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,105,Abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,106,"Ubibutse mugihe yababwira uwo mugenzi wabo ariwe Nuhu (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimuzotinya"
  26,107,Mu vyukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,108,Rero nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,109,"Kandi\tsindabashakira\tko\timpembo,\tmugabo\timpembo\tyanje\tiri k’umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,110,Rero nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire